wi_pre_hdda <- predict(fit_hdda, training)$class
wi_conf_hdda <- caret::confusionMatrix(wi_pre_hdda, training_cls)
print(wi_conf_hdda$table, zero.print = ''); wi_conf_hdda$overall[1]
```

